Detailed Description

Main AUM user object.

This is the main AUM object
  • contains linked list of addresses
  • contains linked list of contexts of addresses
  • contains linked list of group memberships

ASTOBJ_COMPONENTS (  struct  aum_user  ) 
 

Generic pointers - name being one. Name is not a user name, but a user ID code. Only a-z and 0-9, has to begin with character. Not significant in any way, just a handle us
